name: You'll Never Walk Alone
comments: Streisand previously recorded this track before, as part of the medley I Believe/You'll Never Walk Alone for the album Higher Ground . That version was arranged and conducted by Jeremy Lubbock. Streisand recorded the song again with a new arrangement by William Ross . This was the version she sang on her appearance on the Emmy Awards on November 4, 2001.
